## Measure Detection-to-Remediation Time

```spl
index=windows earliest=-30m
(
    EventCode=1006 OR
    EventCode=1007 OR
    EventCode=1116 OR
    EventCode=1117
)
| eval event_type=case(
    EventCode=1006 OR EventCode=1116, "detection",
    EventCode=1007 OR EventCode=1117, "remediation"
)
| stats
    min(eval(if(event_type="detection", _time, null()))) as detection_time
    max(eval(if(event_type="remediation", _time, null()))) as remediation_time
    values(ThreatName) as threat_names
    values(ActionName) as actions
    by host
| eval remediation_delay_seconds=remediation_time-detection_time
| convert ctime(detection_time) ctime(remediation_time)
```

Review results manually when multiple Defender events exist in the same window.

