# Detection Development

## Basic Defender Detection Search

```spl
index=windows earliest=-24h
(
    EventCode=1006 OR
    EventCode=1116
)
| table
    _time
    host
    ThreatName
    SeverityName
    CategoryName
    Path
    DetectionSource
    User
| sort - _time
```

---

## Defender Detection Without Successful Remediation

```spl
index=windows earliest=-24h
(
    EventCode=1006 OR
    EventCode=1007 OR
    EventCode=1008 OR
    EventCode=1116 OR
    EventCode=1117 OR
    EventCode=1118 OR
    EventCode=1119
)
| eval detection=if(EventCode=1006 OR EventCode=1116, 1, 0)
| eval successful_action=if(EventCode=1007 OR EventCode=1117, 1, 0)
| eval failed_action=if(
    EventCode=1008 OR
    EventCode=1118 OR
    EventCode=1119,
    1,
    0
)
| stats
    max(detection) as detected
    max(successful_action) as remediated
    max(failed_action) as remediation_failed
    values(ThreatName) as threat_names
    values(Path) as affected_paths
    by host
| where detected=1 AND (remediated=0 OR remediation_failed=1)
```

This search requires careful time-window and threat-instance correlation.

