## Detection Followed by Defender Disablement

```spl
index=windows earliest=-30m
(
    EventCode=1006 OR
    EventCode=1116 OR
    EventCode=5001
)
| stats
    values(EventCode) as event_codes
    min(_time) as first_seen
    max(_time) as last_seen
    values(ThreatName) as threat_names
    by host
| where mvfind(event_codes, "5001") >= 0
    AND (
        mvfind(event_codes, "1006") >= 0
        OR mvfind(event_codes, "1116") >= 0
    )
| convert ctime(first_seen) ctime(last_seen)
```

This is a higher-priority investigation pattern.

