## Repeated Detection on One Host

```spl
index=windows earliest=-24h
(
    EventCode=1006 OR
    EventCode=1116
)
| stats
    count as detections
    dc(ThreatName) as unique_threats
    values(ThreatName) as threat_names
    values(Path) as paths
    by host
| where detections >= <DETECTION_THRESHOLD>
```

Thresholds should reflect normal testing and software behavior.

