## Wazuh Rule Concept: Defender Detection

```xml
<group name="windows,defender,malware_detection,">
  <rule id="<CUSTOM_RULE_ID>" level="10">
    <field name="win.system.providerName">Microsoft-Windows-Windows Defender</field>
    <field name="win.system.eventID">1006|1116</field>
    <description>Microsoft Defender detected malware or potentially unwanted software</description>
  </rule>
</group>
```

Validate field names against the actual decoded event.

