## Wazuh Rule Concept: Failed Defender Remediation

```xml
<group name="windows,defender,remediation_failure,">
  <rule id="<CUSTOM_RULE_ID>" level="12">
    <field name="win.system.providerName">Microsoft-Windows-Windows Defender</field>
    <field name="win.system.eventID">1008|1118|1119</field>
    <description>Microsoft Defender remediation action failed</description>
  </rule>
</group>
```

A failed remediation event should generally receive higher priority than a successfully remediated test detection.

