## MITRE ATT&CK Context

The Defender detection event itself does not map automatically to one ATT&CK technique.

ATT&CK mapping should be based on the associated behavior, such as:

* T1204 — User Execution
* T1059 — Command and Scripting Interpreter
* T1105 — Ingress Tool Transfer
* T1562.001 — Impair Defenses
* T1547 — Boot or Logon Autostart Execution
* T1486 — Data Encrypted for Impact

The harmless test artifact in this exercise should be labeled as authorized validation activity.

