## Wazuh Does Not Show the Event

Check:

* WIN11TARGET agent status
* Defender Operational channel collection
* Agent configuration
* Decoder
* Rule level
* Dashboard time range
* Agent filter
* Indexer health

Confirm the event exists locally before changing Wazuh.

